headline.main: Jordan Executes 10 Prisoners With Links to Islamic Extremism
headline.print_headline: Jordan Executes 10 With Links to Islamic Extremism

lead_paragraph: The executions were the first since Jordan began a crackdown on Islamist extremists two years ago, in response to the killing of a Jordanian fighter pilot by the Islamic State.
